  "notes": [
    {
      "id": "note-001",
      "title": "Instant Fortress Properties",
      "category": "custom",
      "content": "**Source**: SRD Magic Items - Instant Fortress (p100)\n\n**Dimensions**: 20 feet on a side, 30 feet high\n\n**Structure**:\n- Ground Floor (0-15ft)\n- Second Floor (15-30ft)\n- Roof with battlement (30ft)\n- Ladder, staircase, or ramp connecting floors\n- Trapdoor to roof\n\n**Properties**:\n- **Material**: Adamantine\n- **AC**: 20 (roof, door, walls)\n- **HP**: 100 (each section)\n- **Immunities**: Bludgeoning, Piercing, Slashing (except siege equipment)\n- **Resistances**: All other damage\n- **Special**: Cannot be tipped over (magical)\n\n**Features**:\n- Arrow slits on all sides\n- Battlement atop roof\n- Single door (opens only to attuned user)\n- Immune to Knock spell\n\n**Repair**: Only Wish spell can repair (counts as 8th level spell replication)",
